    public class InMemoryUploadReceiver
extends Object
implements com.vaadin.ui.Upload.Receiver, com.vaadin.ui.Upload.StartedListener, com.vaadin.ui.Upload.ProgressListener
    Generic Upload.Receiver for an Upload component. Stores the bytes in-memory, so be careful to limit the size of the uploads.
    作者:
    Joram Barrez
